          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X00-002D-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-002D-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-X00-002D-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-1" n="1">Three merry Lads you own We are,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-2" n="2">'Tis Very true, and free from Care,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-3" n="3">But envious We cannot bear,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-4" n="4">«LD»Believe Sir:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-5" n="5">For Were all forms of Beauty thine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-6" n="6">Were You like Nireus soft and fine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-7" n="7">We shou'd not in the least repine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-8" n="8">«LD»Or Grieve Sir.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-9" n="9">Then know from us most Beauteous Dan,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-10" n="10">That Roughness best becomes a Man,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-11" n="11">Tis Woman shou'd be pale and Wan</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-12" n="12">«LD»And Taper:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-13" n="13">And all the Triffling Beaux and Fops</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-14" n="14">Who Comb their Brows and sleek their Chaps</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-15" n="15">Are but the Ofspring of Toy shops,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-16" n="16">«LD»Meer Vapour.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-17" n="17">We know Your Morning hours You pass,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-18" n="18">To Cull and gather out a Face</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-19" n="19">Is this the way You take Your Glass?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-20" n="20">«LD»Forbear it:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-21" n="21">Those Loads of Paint upon Your Toilet</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-22" n="22">Will never Mend Your Face but spoil it,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-23" n="23">It looks as if You did par-boil it;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-24" n="24">«LD»Drink Claret.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-25" n="25">Your Cheeks by sleeking are so lean</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-26" n="26">That they're like Cynthia in the Wain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-27" n="27">Or Breast of Goose when 'tis pick'd clean,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-28" n="28">«LD»Or Pullet:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-29" n="29">See What by Prinking You have done</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-30" n="30">Youve Made Your Phyz a skeleton</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-31" n="31">From the long distance of your Crown</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-X00-002D-line-32" n="32">
              <space>To Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>/hi&gt; Gullet.</space>
            </l>
          </lg>
